<chapter xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xml:id="ch-intro">
    <title>Write Once, Read Anywhere</title>
    <objectives>
        <introduction>
            <p>
                At the end of this chapter, you'll
            </p>
        </introduction>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Become aware of the eleven PreTeXt Principles.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
